{"title":"山村宣传队","authors":["路桦"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村宣传队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路桦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传队，进山窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个姑娘四小伙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家当不大装备也不多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两把胡琴加副锣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场院里唱支《学雷锋》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好事儿要比树叶多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里山村学大寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传队敲响开山锣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山挖渠鼓干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战鼓敲进人心窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休息哨子刚吹响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人喊：宣传队，来一个！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长喜来社员夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七嘴八舌笑呵呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说队伍小？谁说嗓门粗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村有了它，闹的热呼呼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}